        "layoutHtml": "<h2 class=\"ielts-listening-question-section-heading\"> Questions 31-40 </h2> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-section-content\"> <div class=\"ielts-listening-section-content-wrapper\"><p>Complete the notes below.</p> <p>Write <strong>ONE WORD ONLY</strong> for each answer.</p> <p class=\"ielts-listening-transcript-subhead\"><strong><strong>DESIGNING A PUBLIC BUILDING:</strong></strong></p> <p class=\"ielts-listening-transcript-subhead\"><strong><strong>THE TAYLOR CONCERT HALL</strong></strong></p> <p><strong>Introduction</strong></p> <p>The designer of a public building may need to consider the building’s</p> <ul> <li>function</li> <li>physical and <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-31\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">31</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_12029_1\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_12029_1\" aria-label=\"Question 31\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span> context</li> <li>symbolic meaning</li> </ul> <p><strong>Location and concept of the Concert Hall</strong></p> <p>On the site of a disused <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-32\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">32</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_12029_2\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_12029_2\" aria-label=\"Question 32\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span></p> <p>Beside a <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-33\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">33</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_12029_3\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_12029_3\" aria-label=\"Question 33\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span></p> <p>The design is based on the concept of a mystery</p> <p><strong>Building design</strong></p> <p>It’s approached by a <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-34\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">34</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_12029_4\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_12029_4\" aria-label=\"Question 34\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span> for pedestrians</p> <p>The building is the shape of a <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-35\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">35</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_12029_5\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_12029_5\" aria-label=\"Question 35\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span></p> <p>One exterior wall acts as a large <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-36\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">36</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_12029_6\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_12029_6\" aria-label=\"Question 36\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span></p> <p>In the auditorium:</p> <ul> <li>the floor is built on huge pads made of <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-37\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">37</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_12029_7\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_12029_7\" aria-label=\"Question 37\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span></li> <li>the walls are made of local wood and are <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-38\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">38</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_12029_8\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_12029_8\" aria-label=\"Question 38\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span> in shape</li> <li>ceiling panels and <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-39\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">39</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_12029_9\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_12029_9\" aria-label=\"Question 39\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span> on walls allow adjustment of acoustics</li> </ul> <p><strong>Evaluation</strong></p> <p>Some critics say the <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-40\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">40</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_12029_10\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_12029_10\" aria-label=\"Question 40\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span> style of the building is inappropriate</p> </div> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-questions\"> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> </div>"
