        "layoutHtml": "<h2 class=\"ielts-listening-question-section-heading\"> Questions 1-10 </h2> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-section-content\"> <p>Complete the table below.</p> <p>Write <strong>ONE WORD AND/OR A NUMBER</strong> for each answer.</p> <p class=\"ielts-listening-transcript-subhead\"><strong><strong>COOKERY CLASSES</strong></strong></p> <table> <tbody> <tr> <td width=\"144\"><strong>Cookery Class</strong></td> <td width=\"192\"><strong>Focus</strong></td> <td width=\"216\"><strong>Other Information</strong></td> </tr> <tr> <td width=\"144\"><em>Example</em><p></p> <p>The Food …<em>Studio</em>…</p></td> <td width=\"192\">how to <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-1\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">1</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_12222_1\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_12222_1\" aria-label=\"Question 1\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span> and cook with seasonal products</td> <td width=\"216\"> <ul> <li>small classes</li> <li>also offers <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-2\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">2</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_12222_2\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_12222_2\" aria-label=\"Question 2\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span> classes</li> <li>clients who return get a <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-3\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">3</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_12222_3\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_12222_3\" aria-label=\"Question 3\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span> discount</li> </ul> </td> </tr> <tr> <td width=\"144\">Bond’s Cookery School</td> <td width=\"192\">food that is <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-4\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">4</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_12222_4\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_12222_4\" aria-label=\"Question 4\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span></td> <td width=\"216\"> <ul> <li>includes recipes to strengthen your <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-5\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">5</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_12222_5\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_12222_5\" aria-label=\"Question 5\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span></li> <li>they have a free <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-6\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">6</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_12222_6\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_12222_6\" aria-label=\"Question 6\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span> Every Thursday</li> </ul> </td> </tr> <tr> <td width=\"144\">The <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-7\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">7</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_12222_7\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_12222_7\" aria-label=\"Question 7\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span> Centre</td> <td width=\"192\">mainly <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-8\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">8</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_12222_8\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_12222_8\" aria-label=\"Question 8\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span> food</td> <td width=\"216\"> <ul> <li>located near the <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-9\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">9</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_12222_9\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_12222_9\" aria-label=\"Question 9\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span></li> <li>a special course in skills with a <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-10\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">10</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_12222_10\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_12222_10\" aria-label=\"Question 10\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span> is sometimes available</li> </ul> </td> </tr> </tbody> </table> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-questions\"> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> </div>"
