        "layoutHtml": "<h2 class=\"ielts-listening-question-section-heading\"> Questions 1-10 </h2> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-section-content\"> <p>Complete the notes below.</p> <p><em>Write <strong>ONE WORD AND/OR A NUMBER</strong> for each answer.</em></p> <table> <tbody> <tr> <td width=\"623\"> <p class=\"ielts-listening-transcript-subhead\"><strong><strong>Moving to Banford City</strong></strong></p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td width=\"623\"><em>Example</em><p></p> <p>Linda recommends living in suburb of: …..<em>Dalton</em>…..</p></td> </tr> <tr> <td width=\"623\"><strong>Accommodation</strong><p></p> <ul> <li>Average rent: £<span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-1\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">1</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_12425_1\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_12425_1\" aria-label=\"Question 1\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span> a month</li> </ul> <p><strong>Transport</strong></p> <ul> <li>Linda travels to work by <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-2\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">2</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_12425_2\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_12425_2\" aria-label=\"Question 2\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span></li> <li>Limited <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-3\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">3</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_12425_3\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_12425_3\" aria-label=\"Question 3\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span> in city centre</li> <li>Trains to London every <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-4\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">4</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_12425_4\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_12425_4\" aria-label=\"Question 4\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span> Minutes</li> <li>Poor train service at <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-5\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">5</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_12425_5\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_12425_5\" aria-label=\"Question 5\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span></li> </ul> <p><strong>Advantages of living in Banford</strong></p> <ul> <li>New <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-6\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">6</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_12425_6\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_12425_6\" aria-label=\"Question 6\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span> opened recently</li> <li><span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-7\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">7</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_12425_7\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_12425_7\" aria-label=\"Question 7\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span> has excellent reputation</li> <li>Good <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-8\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">8</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_12425_8\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_12425_8\" aria-label=\"Question 8\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span> on Bridge Street</li> </ul> <p><strong>Meet</strong> <strong>Linda</strong></p> <ul> <li>Meet Linda on <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-9\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">9</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_12425_9\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_12425_9\" aria-label=\"Question 9\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span> after 5.30 pm</li> <li>In the <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-10\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">10</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_12425_10\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_12425_10\" aria-label=\"Question 10\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span> opposite the station</li> </ul> </td> </tr> </tbody> </table> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-questions\"> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> </div>"
