        "layoutHtml": "<h2 class=\"ielts-listening-question-section-heading\"> Questions 1-10 </h2> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-section-content\"> <div class=\"ielts-listening-section-content-wrapper\"><p><em>Complete the notes below.</em></p> <p><em>Write <strong>ONE WORD AND/OR A NUMBER</strong> for each answer.</em></p> <p class=\"ielts-listening-transcript-subhead\"><strong><strong>Buckworth Conservation Group</strong></strong></p> <p><strong>Regular activities</strong></p> <p>Beach</p> <ul> <li>making sure the beach does not have <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-1\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">1</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_13426_1\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_13426_1\" aria-label=\"Question 1\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span> on it</li> <li>no <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-2\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">2</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_13426_2\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_13426_2\" aria-label=\"Question 2\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span></li> </ul> <p>Nature reserve</p> <ul> <li>maintaining paths</li> <li>nesting boxes for birds installed</li> <li>next task is taking action to attract <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-3\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">3</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_13426_3\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_13426_3\" aria-label=\"Question 3\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span> to the place</li> <li>identifying types of <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-4\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">4</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_13426_4\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_13426_4\" aria-label=\"Question 4\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span></li> <li>building a new <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-5\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">5</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_13426_5\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_13426_5\" aria-label=\"Question 5\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span></li> </ul> <p><strong>Forthcoming events</strong></p> <p>Saturday</p> <ul> <li>meet at Dunsmore Beach car park</li> <li><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">walk across the sands and reach the</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px\"> <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-6\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">6</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_13426_6\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_13426_6\" aria-label=\"Question 6\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span></span></li> <li>take a picnic</li> <li>wear appropriate <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-7\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">7</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_13426_7\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_13426_7\" aria-label=\"Question 7\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span></li> </ul> <p>Woodwork session</p> <ul> <li>suitable for <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-8\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">8</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_13426_8\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_13426_8\" aria-label=\"Question 8\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span> to participate in</li> <li>making <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-9\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">9</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_13426_9\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_13426_9\" aria-label=\"Question 9\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span> out of wood</li> <li>17th, from 10 a.m. to 3 p.m.</li> <li>cost of session (no camping): £<span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-10\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">10</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_13426_10\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_13426_10\" aria-label=\"Question 10\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span></li> </ul> </div> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-questions\"> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> </div>"
