        "layoutHtml": "<h2 class=\"ielts-listening-question-section-heading\"> Questions 1-7 </h2> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-section-content\"> <div class=\"ielts-listening-section-content-wrapper\"><p><em>Complete the notes below.</em></p> <p><em>Write <strong>ONE WORD ONLY</strong> for each answer.</em></p> <p class=\"ielts-listening-transcript-subhead\"><strong><strong>Opportunities for voluntary work in Southoe village</strong></strong></p> <p><strong>Library</strong></p> <ul> <li>Help with <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-1\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">1</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_13541_1\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_13541_1\" aria-label=\"Question 1\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span> books (times to be arranged)</li> <li>Help needed to keep <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-2\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">2</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_13541_2\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_13541_2\" aria-label=\"Question 2\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span> of books up to date</li> <li>Library is in the <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-3\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">3</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_13541_3\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_13541_3\" aria-label=\"Question 3\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span> Room in the village hall</li> </ul> <p><strong>Lunch club</strong></p> <ul> <li>Help by providing <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-4\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">4</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_13541_4\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_13541_4\" aria-label=\"Question 4\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span></li> <li>Help with hobbies such as <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-5\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">5</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_13541_5\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_13541_5\" aria-label=\"Question 5\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span></li> </ul> <p><strong>Help for individuals needed next week</strong></p> <ul> <li>Taking Mrs Carroll to <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-6\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">6</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_13541_6\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_13541_6\" aria-label=\"Question 6\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span></li> <li>Work in the <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-7\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">7</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_13541_7\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_13541_7\" aria-label=\"Question 7\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span> at Mr Selsbury’s house</li> </ul> </div> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-questions\"> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> </div> <h2 class=\"ielts-listening-question-section-heading\"> Questions 8-10 </h2> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-section-content\"> <p><em>Complete the table below.</em></p> <p><em>Write <strong>ONE WORD ONLY</strong> for each answer.</em></p> <table> <tbody> <tr> <td colspan=\"4\" width=\"515\"> <p class=\"ielts-listening-transcript-subhead\"><strong><strong>Village social events</strong></strong></p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td width=\"64\"><strong>Date</strong></td> <td width=\"147\"><strong>Event</strong></td> <td width=\"120\"><strong>Location</strong></td> <td width=\"184\"><strong>Help needed</strong></td> </tr> <tr> <td width=\"64\">19 Oct</td> <td width=\"147\"><span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-8\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">8</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_13543_1\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_13543_1\" aria-label=\"Question 8\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span></td> <td width=\"120\">Village hall</td> <td width=\"184\">providing refreshments</td> </tr> <tr> <td width=\"64\">18 Nov</td> <td width=\"147\">dance</td> <td width=\"120\">Village hall</td> <td width=\"184\">checking <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-9\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">9</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_13543_2\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_13543_2\" aria-label=\"Question 9\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span></td> </tr> <tr> <td width=\"64\">31 Dec</td> <td width=\"147\">New Year’s Eve party</td> <td width=\"120\">Mountfort Hotel</td> <td width=\"184\">designing the <span class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"><strong id=\"ielts-listening-question-number-10\" class=\"ielts-listening-question-number\">10</strong> <input type=\"text\" name=\"ielts_listening_answer_13543_3\" id=\"ielts_listening_answer_13543_3\" aria-label=\"Question 10\" spellcheck=\"false\" autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" value=\"\"></span></td> </tr> </tbody> </table> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-questions\"> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> <div class=\"ielts-listening-question-item\"> </div> </div>"
